{"id": 2392, "genre": 1000, "title": "孩子“犯错\"，你觉哪些纠正方法可能会本末倒置？", "description": "究竟怎样才能做到不伤害不溺爱，又能规范孩子？首先可以了解一下哪些措施是有问题的。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 13502, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201806071828082uojizgVwtL6v3Ad.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-07T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4309, "title": "孩子“犯错\"，你觉哪些纠正方法可能会本末倒置？", "content": "孩子“犯错\"，你觉哪些纠正方法可能会本末倒置？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 285298, "content": "“没收！”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604170350oXkOinK5FyJC3SNI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285299, "content": "“又皮痒了是不是？”“不搞完不许吃饭！”", "image": "img/option/option/201806041704305ry2mpJvEaweFGON.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285301, "content": "“怎么说话呢你这孩子，快当着大家的面给人道歉”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604170519IKHTdcqDL2m1ShQt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285302, "content": "“写个保证书！”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604170636RIAJGoqMXthQTcsr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285303, "content": "“他还是个孩子、长大自然就懂了”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604170753BNzsSjnbxYoDdgUk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285304, "content": "“别让我再逮到/下次再敢XX就XX”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604170952L6XKVYuG5gDbn93T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285305, "content": "“看在你考了 100 分的份上，这次就算了”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604171117TmHGDLCxkpq2dySj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285306, "content": "“没有为什么，不许就是不许”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604171139SwkchmsGv1f8Qr3M.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285307, "content": "“你不用管啦，我已经替你道歉了”", "image": "img/option/option/20180604171324Ova34MgCPFEAVGL6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 285308, "content": "说的事自己也做不到，“你怎么能跟我一样呢”", "image": "img/option/option/